## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Journeys chart, which combines legacy Journey and Pathfinder charts to provide a 360-degree analysis of user conversion paths through products, allowing visualization through Pathfinder, Journey Map, and Top User Paths views with detailed filtering, segmentation, and conversion window options.

